        <briefdescription>
<para>Blanks IS31FL3733 LED display. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>When blank_en is set, the LED display will be disabled. This can be used for flicker-free display updates, or power saving.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>dev</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>LED device structure </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>blank_en</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>should blanking be enabled </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 on success, or negative value on error. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
